commit.message:
Fix list_translations() not to return default locale twice

`list_translations()` was returning the default locale twice if there
was a translation file for the default locale.
Add repository and documentation links to pyproject.toml
Update documentation introduction including links

Do not include documentation files in wheels

Fix the `include` entries in `pyproject.toml` to include documentation
files in sdist format only.  Otherwise, they are added to the top-level
wheel directory and they end up being installed directly
in the top-level site-packages directory, e.g.:

    /usr/lib/python3.11/site-packages/CHANGELOG
    /usr/lib/python3.11/site-packages/LICENSE
    /usr/lib/python3.11/site-packages/README.md
Fix typing that isn't compatible with Python < 3.10.
Bump version: 3.0.0 → 3.0.1
Fix a typo in bumpversion.cfg.
Small fix to ensure get_locale() always returns a Locale object. Fixes #213.
Actually publish the documentation.
